<HEADLINE>
MAKEUP: ALL THAT GLITTERS ISN'T GOLD 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By CYNTHIA ROBINS  
 c.1998 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO _ There is nothing more festive than the flash of
diamonds _ or the seductive shimmer of a high-lighted cheekbone or
the lure of a shoulder swathed in moonlit splendor.
</P>
<P>
   So, if it gleams, glitters, shines or sparkles, and it's not
diamonds, chances are, this holiday, it will show up on cheekbones,
eyelids, collarbones or deep in the decolletage via loose
microscopic foil paillettes, scintillating body gel or shimmer
stick.
</P>
<P>
   For this season's holiday parties and for New Year's Eve,
makeups are about living out your fantasies. Are you Pavlova,
jette-ing through the snow? Or Shiva, shimmering like a goddess in
candlelight? Do you want to twinkle with the exuberance of a
fairy-lit Christmas tree? Or sparkle like a Tiffany treasure?
</P>
<P>
   How you do it is up to you. For subtle shine, try Chanel's
Scintillances, an iridescent all-over body gel that goes where you
want it and stays all evening _ or really glitz it up with Yves
Saint Laurent's Pure Paillette Face Glitter, which captures light
(and attention).
</P>
<P>
   Starting with the eyes, the story is serious moonlight _ all
silvery sheen and glitter. Hard Candy's graphic Techno eyeshadow
has four different ways to gleam and shine with glittery black,
anthracite, iridescent silver and pearlized off-white. Or try
Stila's moon-sparkled single shadows like Moonlight or Starlight.
</P>
<P>
   For far-out fantasy, Yves Saint Laurent has created moonbeams
for the face with three grades of paillettes, ranging from pearly
nacres to silver spangles, brushed onto Blanc d'Argent (a
sparkling, silvery face highlighter). Lancome's micro-paillettes,
meanwhile, add surprise sparkle to the hair.
</P>
<P>
   So you glow, girl. And glitter. And shine. And sparkle all you
like. Maybe your significant other will take the hint and buy you
the real thing.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-12-22-98 1255EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
