<P>
   IMPEACH-LAW-FIRM _ WASHINGTON _ If there is a quick solution to
President Clinton's jeopardy in the Senate, it may emerge from the
offices of Verner Liipfert, widely considered the capital's most
influential law firm. The star-studded roster of partners and
associates includes former Sens. Bob Dole and George Mitchell _
already involved in censure discussions _ and former Gov. Ann
Richards of Texas. (Dart, Cox News Service).
