   &UR; ENTERTAINMENT: &LR;  (Available by 2 p.m., Wed., Dec. 23) More than
a movie, ``Prince of Egypt,'' the animated musical that retells the
story of Moses, is an impressive watch-your-back gesture to Jeffrey
Katzenberg's old employer, Walt Disney Studios, where Katzenberg
spent 10 years reviving its faded pen-and-ink wing.
</P>
