everything we can. We charge the rest. We begin to wonder not how
we can ever get ahead in our financial lives but how we can just
catch up. The truth is, getting ahead is not that hard. What you
have to do to get started is to save money. That's not
overwhelmingly hard, either. What's hard is making yourself do it.
