<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-22 21:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3166 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AMAZON-SHIPPING-ART-2     12-22 0650
